  <steps>
    <step num="0">In a medium bowl, soak raw hazelnuts in 2 cups (475 ml) of water overnight. </step>
    <step num="1">Drain the bowl of water and place the hazelnuts in a blender. </step>
    <step num="2">Add 1 tablespoon vanilla, 2 tablespoons honey, 2 tablespoons unsweetened cacao powder, 1 pinch of salt, and 4 cups (945 ml) of water to the blender. </step>
    <step num="3">Blend the mixture on high for 90 seconds. </step>
    <step num="4">Use a cheesecloth to strain the liquid into a pouring container. </step>
    <step num="5">(Optional) refrigerate 1-2 hours or serve immediately. </step>
    <step num="6">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
